KitKat::

She was finished.  She opened the door to the chamber and stepped 
out.  Her shiney black body was clean and looked like new. She 
transformed into wolf mode and back to bot  She smiled at the male 
bot infront of her. "I thank you for saving me."  He bowed to the 
bot. "May I have the name of the champion who rescued me from the 
jaws of death?"
